{"tid":119070,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"現時年輕人所處於既社會係你地班廢老所造成既","createTime":"2017-02-13T13:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T01:45:02.000Z","uid":2641,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e806580ab3471bd152f21144e679add9e12d3fdf","tid":119070,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"如題，所有制度、環境、風氣等等都係你地一手一腳造成，年輕人、小朋友都係係一個充滿你地影子既社會中成長，自自然然呢班人所表現到出黎既嘢其實就係你地班廢老既一部分。<br />\n<br />\n當年輕人係呢個社會遇到難題，甚至社會出現問題，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請問你班廢老憑d咩去怪責班年輕人呀？</span></span>所有野都係你地種出黎既因呀屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n相反，希望你地見到呢幾句怨氣既時候，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該你班仆街好好反省同檢討下點解呢個社會會搞成咁，而唔係擺出一副看破紅塵、事不關己既撚樣呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"edce55266477cc7633784f52e6757e3965690f60","tid":119070,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07dc0f2e1b2732f4d68a0568c9b79e1bd7cd0136","tid":119070,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:05:23.000Z","msg":"漏左唔記得講，我唔係話年輕人冇任何問題，只不過你班廢老唔好將責任推卸得一乾二淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每個年代都有每個年代既問題，你地遇到既問題唔好用黎鬥慘，要怪就怪自己上一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38833e0b60bef3728f70eeb5655e8abfecd7a7b2","tid":119070,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838b9724aedc07c372763458e9eb4badc147a035","tid":119070,"uid":33572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"要搶後生福利<br />\n要人讓座<br />\n要搶公屋<br